https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Musical - Rat Packer and star of the original Ocean's Eleven, Dean Martin forged his mark in the entertainment world as an actor, straight man to Jerry Lewis and a crooner who made ladies swoon. This collection features Martin singing swing and 1950s standards from top pop, jazz and Broadway composers such as Lerner and Lowe ("Almost Like Being in Love"), Louis Prima ("Oh Marie, Oh Marie") and Rodgers and Hart ("It's Easy to Remember"). - Henry Stephens Dean Martin: Memories Are Made of This
